room_title: Escape room "The Awakening" by Escape Mission Chattanooga in Chattanooga
room_description:
There have been some strange things happening at Keystone Cemetery ever since it's caretaker passed of a sudden illness. Some say it is haunted by those laid to rest, others have reported to seeing nefarious late night visitors. Your group's mission is to investigate the Keystone Cemetery and put it all together...
Be warned! Those who overstay their welcome, never return to tell their tale...
